column2: SELECT TOP #   s.ra, s.dec,       s.z, s.zErr,   s.velDisp, s.velDispErr,   s.snMedian,      l.EW_Hb_#, l.EW_Hb_#_Err, l.Flux_Hb_#, l.Flux_Hb_#_Err, l.Flux_Cont_Hb_#, l.Flux_Cont_Hb_#_Err,   l.EW_Ha_#, l.EW_Ha_#_Err, l.Flux_Ha_#, l.Flux_Ha_#_Err, l.Flux_Cont_Ha_#, l.Flux_Cont_Ha_#_Err,   l.V_Ha_#, l.V_Ha_#_Err, l.Sigma_Ha_#, l.Sigma_Ha_#_Err,      mpa.lgm_tot_p5# as lgm, (mpa.lgm_tot_p8#-mpa.lgm_tot_p1#)/#. as lgm_Err,   mpa.sfr_tot_p5# as lsfr, (mpa.sfr_tot_p8#-mpa.sfr_tot_p1#)/#. as lsfr_Err,    INTO mydb.methclass FROM SpecObj AS s ON n.objid=s.bestobjid   JOIN emissionLinesPort as l ON s.specobjid=l.specobjid JOIN galSpecExtra as mpa on s.specobjid=mpa.specobjid
